        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <h2>Hello, I'm <span>Bindu</span></h2>
    <p>Pursuing <b>3rd year B.Tech</b> at <b>Srinivasa Ramanujan Institute of Technology</b>.  
    I build modern cyberpunk-style web designs using HTML & CSS.</p>
</section>

<div class="container" id="about">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>I am a frontend enthusiast interested in futuristic UI, neon themes, and smooth web animations.</p>
</div>

<div class="container" id="skills">
    <h2>Basic Skills</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>HTML – Semantic structure</li>
        <li>CSS – Layouts & neon themes</li>
        <li>Responsive Web Design</li>
        <li>Flexbox positioning</li>
        <li>Basic UI/UX</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="container" id="projects">
    <h2>Projects</h2>
    <div class="projects">
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>Cyberpunk Portfolio</h3>
            <p>Neon themed futuristic UI.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>Landing Page</h3>
            <p>Modern and colorful web layout.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>UI Practice</h3>
            <p>Flexbox, alignment, animated elements.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container" id="contact">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> bindu@example.com</p>
    <p><strong>Phone:</strong> 9876543210</p>
    <p><strong>Location:</strong> India</p>

    <div class="social-icons">
        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a>
        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
        <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    © 2025 Bindu — All Rights Reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
